:{{DIcon|Talk}} How many people have had their pain "soothed" by you?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500207119-->
::'''Capote:''' I'm not someone who likes to reap benefits for myself, and I hope you understand that.
::'''Capote:''' But since you asked, I will answer &mdash; After all, my life's duty is to dispel others' confusion!
::'''Capote:''' Do you see the burning gazes of the fans around us? Those passionate looks of rapture are the best evidence of having had their pains soothed!
::'''Capote:''' They no longer have their eyes clouded and now see the stars, and that is how they are able to passionately look at me... I mean, at truth and reality!
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} The way you move seems to be deliberately designed...
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500207124-->
::'''Capote:''' I understand what you mean. Many people have told me the same thing.
::'''Capote:''' People always get attracted by my body language and my eyes. I find it really frustrating.
::'''Capote:''' No matter how hard I try to refrain myself and avoid causing trouble for others, it never works.
::'''Capote:''' Maybe it's just a part of me that's beyond my control.
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Talk}} What do you think about this invasion?
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500207129-->
::'''Capote:''' A disaster! An absolute, complete disaster!
::'''Capote:''' I know that everyone on the space station is concerned these days and all hold different views regarding the invasion.
::'''Capote:''' However, I only see the horrified faces of my fans. Though roses moist with tears hold a special scent, it would be apocalyptic for such thick and sweet aromas to turn sour with sorrow.
::'''Capote:''' Therefore, I need to remain steadfast in my duty, and become their guiding light!
:;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
:{{DIcon|Exit}} I don't have any other questions.
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500207135-->
::'''Capote:''' If you still hold confusion in your heart, please, come find me anytime. Of course, you may also write to me. I like that kind of classical communication method.
::'''Capote:''' You can give your letter to Lamina and she will look after it. I look forward to seeing you again &mdash; or seeing your letters.
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
