::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What are you doing here?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500207105-->
:::'''Capote:''' Oh! Here's another lost soul. Don't worry. I'll show you the way.
:::'''Capote:''' My name is Capote. I'm a member of the Department of Ecology, but my other identity is even more important...
:::'''Capote:''' I am a die-hard fan of Madam Herta!
:::'''Capote:''' I'm here to make my humble contributions to this space station, as well as to Madam Herta.
:::'''Capote:''' Though I cannot fight against these horrors and lay out a road to revival...
:::'''Capote:''' But with my words, I will guide all those who are lost and in a panic like yourself.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} How can you help me?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_500207112-->
:::'''Capote:''' Help? Right, you do look like you need some help.
:::'''Capote:''' I can see anxiety in your eyes. This emotion originates from fear. I can understand it.
:::'''Capote:''' And I will clear the uncertainty in your heart. This is the least I can do for Madam Herta.
:::'''Capote:''' Come! Confess it all to me! Tell me all your frustrations and pain, and let me soothe them for you!
:::'''Capote:''' *cough* Of course, this is just psychological help. If you feel any real discomfort, please seek out a medical doctor.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
